title: Bob Marley (Comedian) - All New Stuff
description:
NOT the reggae singer-this Bob Marley is the comedian from Maine.  He&#039;s had several CDs of his stand up, 3 DVDs, and bit parts in a few movies, including Boondock Saints.  These first few albums are hilarious if you&#039;re familiar with Maine at all, but they&#039;re also pretty damn funny if you&#039;re not.  I&#039;d say he&#039;s one of the best stand up comedians working today.
Give it a try-if there&#039;s any interest, I have quite a few more of his albums.
